Title: Living Room
Text: I reach the living room. There is so much stuff here that i almost can't walk. It has a big fucking TV. This must be paired with a nice sound system.
There is also a lot of places to sit. A big couch with the almost same length as the living room. As i reach the living room, the noise suddenly stops. I could not find is origin.
I could also see the dining room and the kitchen. They seem empty but i should check booth
